node.text:
The full line up of Apples larger iPhone models.

Yes I like a big smartphone. I like the size the extra weight and the increased screen and the bigger battery’s that get me through a full days use. These are all features I expect from a Plus or Max model. Something about feeling a phone in your pocket and the weight in your hand to me gives it a more premium feel.🤩

I totally understand that these larger models are not everyone’s cup of tea.
But I love them 📱😉
Source: @mav__tech
